<p>
  <strong>2006-12-15</strong><br/>
  The phpMyFAQ Team would like to announce the availability of
  <a href="/download">phpMyFAQ 1.6.8</a>. This release fixes some serious
  security issues like SQL injection and remote code execution. All users of affected phpMyFAQ versions
  are encouraged to upgrade as soon as possible to this latest versions! A detailed
  <a href="/security/advisory-2006-12-15">security advisory</a> is available. We also fixed the blank dropdown
  issue when installing phpMyFAQ for the first time and some minor bugs.
</p>
